entry.title: New release for Cal.com: v4.5.10

  • fix: make theme logic safe and add better e2e tests by @hbjORbj in https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/pull/16959
  • fix: booker atom phone booking field by @supalarry in https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/pull/16945
  • fix: add suppressHydrationWarning to app router layout by @hbjORbj in https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/pull/16960
  • refactor: v2 throttler guard by @supalarry in https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/pull/16922

  • feat: update translations by @calcom-bot in https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/pull/16972
  • fix: SMS reminders are being sent out with HTML code by @anikdhabal in https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/pull/16966
  • chore: remove log in settings/my-account/conferencing by @hbjORbj in https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/pull/16981
  • chore: add dev docs on mintlify by @alishaz-polymath in https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/pull/16935
  • perf: Only render the TimezoneChangeDialog when needed by @emrysal in https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/pull/16986
  • refactor: platform bookings hooks & bookings API by @supalarry in https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/pull/16963
  • fix: Salesforce assign event to organizer by @joeauyeung in https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/pull/16971
  • chore: remove react code in getLayout by @hbjORbj in https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/pull/16997
  • refactor: throttler rate limits for oauth client & access token by @supalarry in https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/pull/16962

  • feat: Attribute based routing from Team Routing Form to Team Event(with assigned users matching the attribute logic) by @hariombalhara in https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/pull/16823
  • feat: update translations by @calcom-bot in https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/pull/16999
  • fix: Close OOO Create Modal on backdrop click by @hbjORbj in https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/pull/17000
  • chore: revert /settings/my-account app router by @hbjORbj in https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/pull/17002
  • chore: Update PR template to account for new docs by @keithwillcode in https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/pull/17003
  • fix: add fallback to data needed in SettingsLayout by @hbjORbj in https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/pull/17004
  • chore: v4.5.10 by @keithwillcode in https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/pull/17001
